'''林良铭'''{{BD|1997年|6月4日||}} (''粵拼：Lam4 Leung4 Ming4'')，出生于[[广东省|广东省]][[汕头市|汕头市]]，中国职业[[足球|足球]]运动员，司职左中場。出自[[广州富力|广州富力]]青训，曾入选国少队和国青队。

林良铭曾入选了[[李明_(1971年)|李明]]挂帅的U19国青队，参加过斯洛伐克八国青年锦标赛和里斯本四国赛的比赛，且在这两项赛事总共打进三球成为国青队内的头号得分手。

2015年夏季，林良铭從[[广州富力|广州富力]]以22万欧元的转会费轉會至[[西班牙|西班牙]]豪门[[皇家马德里|皇家马德里]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.qq.com/a/20150723/025211.htm |title=曝皇马30万欧签下林良铭 富力：从未联系过我们 |access-date=2015-10-06 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206121119/https://sports.qq.com/a/20150723/025211.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>林良銘是首位加盟皇家馬德里的[[亞洲人|亞洲]]球员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/china/j/2015-08-06/doc-ifxftkpe2698151.shtml |title=180万变22万!皇马强挖林良铭 富力吃哑巴亏 |access-date=2015-10-06 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825143131/http://sports.sina.com.cn/china/j/2015-08-06/doc-ifxftkpe2698151.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.realmadrid.com/en/football/academy/under-19/lin-liangming |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-10-13 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123190526/https://www.realmadrid.com/en/football/academy/under-19/lin-liangming |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefayouthleague/season=2016/clubs/player=250090123/index.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-10-13 |archive-date=2018-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001113933/https://www.uefa.com/uefayouthleague/season=2016/clubs/player=250090123/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年租借到[[阿尔梅里亚体育联盟|阿尔梅里亚体育联盟]]。2019年加盟[[马里迪莫体育俱乐部|马里迪莫]]，但仅代表U23队出场7次。2020年租借加盟[[大连人职业足球俱乐部|大连人职业足球俱乐部]]<ref name="titan1">{{cite web |author1=金山淞 |title=林良铭租借加盟大连人 贝尼特斯上任伊始点名买他 |url=http://www.titan24.com/publish/app/data/2020/02/28/306271/os_news.html#:~:text=%E9%9A%8F%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%98%E5%AE%A3%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%8D%AE%E6%82%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E4%BB%A5%E7%A7%9F%E5%80%9F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%90%83%E9%98%9F%E3%80%82,%E2%80%9C2020%E5%B9%B42%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E4%B8%8E%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E8%BF%AA%E8%8E%AB%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A1%E5%A4%9A%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%8A%E7%90%83%E5%91%98%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%8F%E5%95%86%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8E%E7%90%83%E5%91%98%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E7%AD%BE%E7%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E4%BB%A5%E7%A7%9F%E5%80%9F%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%9E%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E3%80%82 |website=体坛网 |accessdate=2021-08-16 |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816071434/http://www.titan24.com/publish/app/data/2020/02/28/306271/os_news.html#:~:text=%E9%9A%8F%E5%8D%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%98%E5%AE%A3%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%8D%AE%E6%82%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%97%E8%89%AF%E9%93%AD%E4%BB%A5%E7%A7%9F%E5%80%9F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F%E7%90%83%E9%98%9F%E3%80%82,%E2%80%9C2020%E5%B9%B42%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E4%B8%8E%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E8%BF%AA%E8%8E%AB%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A1%E5%A4%9A%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%94%E4%BF%B1%E4%B9%90%E9%83%